{"tid":2098103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★醫學會傳染病顧問：不排除碗碟亦可傳播病毒。","createTime":"2020-07-07T08:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T10:11:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22b9f0f154a94258ad02f6f2385e49997e1a5f24","tid":2098103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:52:31.000Z","msg":"本地新冠肺炎感染群組再現，彩虹坪石邨「彬記粥麵美食」或出現群組爆發；香港醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超批評港府政策未到位，入境限制措施現漏洞，豁免指定人士檢疫，吸引不少人員在港轉機、轉船，增加本地爆發風險，致本港出現第三波社區爆發。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超認為，確診廚師未必直接接觸到食客，惟廚師會與其他店內職員接觸，亦不能排除碗碟亦可傳播病毒。他提醒食客宜避免在空氣流通欠佳的餐廳與他人近距離「搭枱」，否則風險會較大。<br />\n<br />\n而香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何柏良亦提醒，倘確診者工作期間沒戴口罩，或致本港多區在數天內出現個案，直言本港疫情「亮紅燈」，港府應呼籲高危場所（如食店）負責人嚴謹採取防疫措施，分隔食客、洗淨餐具，另可提供熱水供食客在用膳前再沖洗餐具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/494759/%E6%A2%81%E5%AD%90%E8%B6%85-%E6%88%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%B3%A2%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%88%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E5%A0%B5%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F494759%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25A0%2588%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B1%2581%25E5%2585%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=cc7c9d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/494759/%E6%A2%81%E5%AD%90%E8%B6%85-%E6%88%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%B3%A2%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%88%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E5%A0%B5%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E</a>"},{"pid":"338cef2c38eecc948d1269140860ef974e03f49f","tid":2098103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df4b30c57d5974924fb4918c5a5a6d0949aeb25","tid":2098103,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"熱飲隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85912d90d52b3cf3782c9851abf228f2f4ae2314","tid":2098103,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>近日新增大量本地確診</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家出街一定要戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n勤力洗手<br />\n<br />\n唔好去人多既地方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望政府可以立即停課，收緊限聚令，停gym房，戲院，k房等</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a7162b1376c447d6d89afe4ac71eb7b16baee0a","tid":2098103,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"環保撚去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5cb2669547ed401b746a3e2136e2dc2c26f04f","tid":2098103,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a7162b1376c447d6d89afe4ac71eb7b16baee0a","tid":2098103,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"環保撚去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"「無辦法